---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="footer">
	<div class="inner">
		<div class="colophon">
			<p class="motto">
				<em>An editorial library</em> for key-value storage, set in
				<a href="https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Instrument+Serif" rel="noopener">Instrument Serif</a>
				and
				<a href="https://vercel.com/font" rel="noopener">Geist</a>.
			</p>
			<p class="legal">
				MIT © {year} <a href="https://github.com/ambicuity" rel="noopener">Ritesh Rana</a>.
				All adapters ship under the same license.
			</p>
			<p class="patron-line">
				If Storely saved you time, you can
				<a href="https://buymeacoffee.com/ritesh.rana" rel="noopener" class="patron-link">
					<svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="13" height="13" aria-hidden="true">
						<path
							d="M3 7h9.5a1.5 1.5 0 0 1 0 3H12M3 7v4a3 3 0 0 0 3 3h3a3 3 0 0 0 3-3v-1M5 4c0-.6.4-1 1-1M7 4c0-.6.4-1 1-1M9 4c0-.6.4-1 1-1"
							stroke="currentColor"
							stroke-width="1.2"
							fill="none"
							stroke-linecap="round"
						/>
					</svg>
					buy me a coffee
				</a>.
			</p>
		</div>

		<div class="links">
			<section>
				<h4>Project</h4>
				<ul>
					<li><a href="https://github.com/ambicuity/storely" rel="noopener">Repository</a></li>
					<li><a href="https://github.com/ambicuity/storely/blob/main/CHANGELOG.md" rel="noopener">Changelog</a></li>
					<li><a href="https://github.com/ambicuity/storely/blob/main/SECURITY.md" rel="noopener">Security policy</a></li>
				</ul>
			</section>
			<section>
				<h4>Learn</h4>
				<ul>
					<li><a href="/docs/getting-started/">Getting started</a></li>
					<li><a href="/adapters/">Storage adapters</a></li>
					<li><a href="/third-party/">Third-party adapters</a></li>
				</ul>
			</section>
			<section>
				<h4>Support</h4>
				<ul>
					<li>
						<a href="https://buymeacoffee.com/ritesh.rana" rel="noopener" class="support">
							Buy me a coffee
						</a>
					</li>
					<li><a href="https://github.com/sponsors/ambicuity" rel="noopener">GitHub Sponsors</a></li>
					<li><a href="https://github.com/ambicuity/storely/issues" rel="noopener">Report an issue</a></li>
				</ul>
			</section>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="bar">
		<span>Built with care · No tracking · No cookies</span>
		<span class="rule" aria-hidden="true"></span>
		<span>storely.org</span>
	</div>
</footer>

<style>
	.footer {
		border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
		margin-top: 6rem;
		background: var(--canvas);
	}

	.inner {
		max-width: 1320px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 3rem var(--margin) 1.6rem;
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 2fr 3fr;
		gap: var(--gutter);
	}

	@media (max-width: 720px) {
		.inner {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}

	.colophon {
		max-width: 32rem;
	}

	.motto {
		font-family: var(--font-display);
		font-size: var(--step-2);
		line-height: 1.3;
		letter-spacing: var(--tracking-tight);
		color: var(--ink);
	}

	.motto em {
		font-style: italic;
		color: var(--accent);
	}

	.motto a {
		color: var(--ink);
		border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
	}

	.legal {
		margin-top: 1.4rem;
		font-size: var(--step--1);
		color: var(--ink-soft);
	}

	.legal a {
		color: inherit;
		border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
	}

	.links {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
		gap: var(--gutter);
	}

	@media (max-width: 720px) {
		.links {
			grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 480px) {
		.links {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}

	.patron-line {
		margin-top: 1.4rem;
		font-family: var(--font-display);
		font-style: italic;
		font-size: var(--step-1);
		line-height: 1.4;
		color: var(--ink-soft);
		max-width: 28rem;
	}

	.patron-link {
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.35rem;
		color: var(--accent);
		border-bottom: 1px solid var(--accent);
		padding-bottom: 1px;
		font-style: italic;
		transition: border-bottom-width var(--dur-fast) var(--ease-out);
	}

	.patron-link:hover {
		border-bottom-width: 2px;
	}

	.links a.support {
		color: var(--accent);
	}

	.links a.support:hover {
		color: var(--accent-soft);
	}

	.links h4 {
		font-family: var(--font-body);
		font-weight: 500;
		font-size: var(--step--2);
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: var(--tracking-caps);
		color: var(--ink-faint);
		margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
	}

	.links ul {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 0.35rem;
		font-size: var(--step--1);
	}

	.links a {
		color: var(--ink-soft);
		transition: color var(--dur-fast) var(--ease-out);
	}

	.links a:hover {
		color: var(--accent);
	}

	.bar {
		border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
		padding: 0.8rem var(--margin);
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 1rem;
		max-width: 1320px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		font-family: var(--font-mono);
		font-size: var(--step--2);
		color: var(--ink-faint);
		letter-spacing: 0.04em;
	}

	.bar .rule {
		flex: 1;
		height: 1px;
		background: var(--rule);
	}
</style>
